  "lyrics": {
    "v1": "Far, far away on Judea&#39;s plains, Shepherds of old heard the joyous strains: Glory to God, glory to God, Glory to God in the highest; Peace on earth, good will to men; Peace on earth, good will to men.",
    "v2": "Sweet are these strains of redeeming love, Message of mercy from heaven above: highest; Peace on earth, good will to men; Peace on earth, good will to men.",
    "v3": "Lord, with the angels we too would rejoice; Help us to sing with the heart and voice: highest; Peace on earth, good will to men; Peace on earth, good will to men.",
    "v4": "Hasten the time when, from every clime, Men shall unite in the strains sublime: highest; Peace on earth, good will to men; Peace on earth, good will to men."
  },
